01:30:59.997 --> 01:31:03.208
Ah, honey, you hit me.

01:31:03.250 --> 01:31:04.960
Shit, are you okay?

01:31:05.878 --> 01:31:08.046
No, no, I'm not.

01:31:08.922 --> 01:31:09.882
I haven't slept in days.

01:31:09.923 --> 01:31:12.718
