privacy with my students.

01:31:15.804 --> 01:31:16.680
I'm terrible.

01:31:16.722 --> 01:31:17.389
Sam.

01:31:17.431 --> 01:31:18.765
No, no, I need to say something.

01:31:18.807 --> 01:31:22.936
